<header>
<product>DX</product>
<table>DX.EVENT.TYPE</table>
</header>
<overview>
<ovdesc>

            <p>This application holds details of all of the procesing / accounting events that can occur in the derivatives modules.</p>
            <p />
            <p>      By default this application does not come pre-setup as the user must consider the impact of each events setup.</p>
            <p />
            <p>      The following is a list of items that should be setup.</p>
            <p />
            <p> ID "Event Description"</p>
            <p> AR Contract Assignment (Rev)</p>
            <p> AS Contract Assignment</p>
            <p> BV Back Valuation</p>
            <p> CA Contract Amendment</p>
            <p> CC Contract Cancellation</p>
            <p> CD Unauth Contract Deletion</p>
            <p> CI Contract Inception</p>
            <p> CM Contract Maturity</p>
            <p> CN Internal Transfer</p>
            <p> CO External Transfer</p>
            <p> CP Corporate Action</p>
            <p> CR Contract Amendment (Reversal)</p>
            <p> CS Contract Settlement</p>
            <p> CT Incoming Transfer</p>
            <p> CU Unauth Contract Amendment</p>
            <p> CX Corporate Action (Rev)</p>
            <p> ER Contract Exercise (Rev)</p>
            <p> ET European Financial Transaction Tax</p>
            <p> EX Contract Exercise</p>
            <p> FC Commission posting</p>
            <p> FE Execution fee/csn posting</p>
            <p> FL Clearing fee/csn posting</p>
            <p> FM Misc fee posting</p>
            <p> FR Regulatory fee posting</p>
            <p> IM Initial Margin</p>
            <p> OA Order Amendment</p>
            <p> OB Order Blocking</p>
            <p> OC Order Cancellation (Reversal)</p>
            <p> OD Order Deletion</p>
            <p> OF Order Fill</p>
            <p> OI Order Input</p>
            <p> OM Option Variation Margin</p>
            <p> OR Order Stage Superseded</p>
            <p> OX Order Abandon</p>
            <p> PC Closed position</p>
            <p> PO Open position</p>
            <p> PP Premium Posting</p>
            <p> PY Cash Payment</p>
            <p> RO Realised Option P and L</p>
            <p> RP Realised P and L</p>
            <p> SR Settlement Reversal</p>
            <p> TT Tax posting</p>
            <p> UO Unrealised Option P and L</p>
            <p> VM Variation Margin</p>
            <p> XO Exotic Event</p>
            <p> XO-XYZ Exotic Event for OPTION.TYPE "XYZ" *</p>
            <p> XP Contract Expiry</p>
            <p> XR Contract Expiry (Rev)</p>
            <p />
            <p> * Can set up specific event types for each exotic option type defined in OPTION.TYPE.</p>
        </ovdesc>
<ovimage></ovimage>
</overview>
