<t>
<field>USE.FT.TXN.CODE</field>
<desc>
            <p>If this event is associated with FT.CHARGE.TYPE or FT.COMMISSION.TYPE record (i.e. entered or defaulted in DX.TRADE), use the txn codes and category from those tables, if NO overridewith the codes entered in DX.EVENT.TYPE= YES-NO.</p>
