<t>
<field>EB.ACTIVITY</field>
<desc>
            <p>EB.ACTIVITY is the activity that takes place in all T24 applications using soft delivery. The Derivatives module uses the events in DX.EVENT.TYPE to generate the hand off records. (records for delivery.)</p>
            <p>
                <p>Validation Rules:</p>
            </p>
            <p />
            <p />
            <p>      Must be set in EB.ACTIVITY a 4 digit numeric code         definning each activity.</p>
            <p />
            <p />
            <p>      E.g. DX-0202 for Derivatives (premium for options)</p>
        </desc>
