<t>
<field>CATEGORY</field>
<desc>
            <p>CATEGORY code used for posting the entries. This can be either an internal account category code or a profit and loss category code range depnding upon the type of contract event. A field validation is provided to determin whether a profit and loss category code to accepted or an internal account category code.</p>
            <p>
                <p>Validation Rules:</p>
            </p>
            <p />
            <p />
            <p>      Up to 5 character, input must exist on the CATEGORY  application</p>
            <p>      Mandatory for events requiring a category code for </p>
            <p>      P/L reporting or internal account set up</p>
            <p />
            <p />
            <p>The following EVENT.TYPE falls under Category Code  range of '10000-19999' </p>
            <p />
            <p>'IM','CA','CC','CI','SR','CU','PO',PC','RO','OI','OA','OC','OD','OX','OB','AM','FX','CR'</p>
            <p />
            <p />
            <p />
            <p>The following EVENT.TYPE falls under the Category Code range of '50000-59999' </p>
            <p />
            <p>'CM','CS','FC','FE','FR','FL','FM','RP','VM','OM','BP','TT','PY','ET'</p>
            <p />
            <P />
            <p>Apart from these there are two EVENT.TYPE which accepts two different range</p>
            <p />
            <p> 'PP' = '10000-19999' and '50000-59999' </p>
            <p> 'UO' = '24000-24999' and '50000-59999' </p>
        </desc>
</t>
<t>
